point A at (100, 100)
point B at (300, 200)
point C at (200, 300)

triangle T passes_through A B C

angle_bisector BisA of B A C
angle_bisector BisB of A B C
angle_bisector BisC of A C B

segment AB of A B
segment BC of B C
segment AC of A C

label A "Vertex A"
label B "Vertex B"
label C "Vertex C"
label BisA "Bisector A"